comments: Caldwell-Pope (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and the contact is marginal.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Kuzma (WAS) makes contact with Giddey's (OKC) body that affects his play at the basket.
Dort (OKC) makes contact to the ball and marginal contact to Beal's (WAS) arm as he swipes down to defend the pass.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) makes contact to Giddey's (OKC) body on the drive that affects his SBQR.
Caldwell-Pope (WAS) sets the pick on Dort (OKC) from a wide stance and there is marginal leg to leg contact that is caused by Caldwell-Pope.
Giddey (OKC) reaches in and makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Avdija (WAS) makes marginal contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Robinson-Earl (OKC) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) takes a dribble before the Thunder signal for and are granted the timeout request, therefore they are not allowed to advance the ball coming out of the timeout.
